    "/posms/app2app": {
      "get": {
        "operationId": "app2app-integration",
        "tags": [
          "POSMS"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "Authorization",
            "in": "header",
            "description": "Bearer token for APP2APP HTTP protocol. Example: 'Bearer <your_token>'",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "example": "Bearer 97ed54e0adf46543b491365c27cb5290"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "APP2APP Integration Documentation",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object"
                },
                "examples": {
                  "response": {
                    "value": {
                      "message": "OK",
                      "code": 200,
                      "current_time": "2025-05-28T12:00:00+0200"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "summary": "APP2APP Integration",
        "description": "La integraci\u00f3n APP2APP permite a su aplicaci\u00f3n m\u00f3vil comunicarse directamente con el servicio Sentinel de Paylands para procesar pagos a trav\u00e9s de dispositivos f\u00edsicos. Este enfoque es perfecto para negocios que ya tienen aplicaciones m\u00f3viles y desean a\u00f1adir capacidades de pago sin implementar toda la l\u00f3gica de comunicaci\u00f3n con el dispositivo.\n\nExisten dos protocolos de comunicaci\u00f3n principales:\n1. **Protocolo HTTP**: Para comunicaci\u00f3n directa con el terminal de pago mediante llamadas HTTP a http://<Direcci\u00f3n>:6889/sentinel\n2. **Operaci\u00f3n Intent (Android)**: Para aplicaciones Android que utilizan comunicaci\u00f3n basada en intents con el formato URI: com.paynopain.sentinel://<M\u00e9todo>?<Datos>\n\nOperaciones disponibles:\n- [Pago](/posms/app2app/payment): Procesa un pago a trav\u00e9s de un dispositivo f\u00edsico\n- [Devoluci\u00f3n](/posms/app2app/refund): Procesa una devoluci\u00f3n a una tarjeta previamente cobrada\n- [GetTransaction](/posms/app2app/transaction): Obtiene informaci\u00f3n sobre una transacci\u00f3n espec\u00edfica\n- [Card Verify](/posms/app2app/card-verify): Verifica una tarjeta sin procesar un pago\n\nPara obtener documentaci\u00f3n completa sobre cada operaci\u00f3n, consulte las secciones espec\u00edficas de este documento o utilice los enlaces de operaci\u00f3n proporcionados.",
        "x-description-i18n": {
          "eng": "The APP2APP integration allows your mobile application to communicate directly with the Paylands Sentinel Service for processing payments through physical devices. This approach is perfect for businesses with existing mobile applications that want to integrate payment capabilities without implementing all the low-level device communication logic.\n\nThere are two main communication protocols:\n1. **HTTP Protocol**: For direct HTTP communication with the payment terminal at http://<Address>:6889/sentinel\n2. **Intent Operation (Android)**: For Android applications using intent-based communication with URI format: com.paynopain.sentinel://<Method>?<Data>\n\nAvailable operations:\n- [Payment](/posms/app2app/payment): Process a payment through a physical device\n- [Refund](/posms/app2app/refund): Process a refund to a previously charged card\n- [GetTransaction](/posms/app2app/transaction): Retrieve information about a specific transaction\n- [Card Verify](/posms/app2app/card-verify): Verify a card without processing a payment\nFor comprehensive documentation on each operation, see the specific sections of this document or use the operation links provided."
        },
        "x-summary-i18n": {
          "eng": "APP2APP Integration"
        }
      }
    },
    "/posms/app2app/payment": {
      "post": {
        "operationId": "app2app-payment",
        "tags": [
          "POSMS - APP2APP"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "$ref": "#/paths/~1posms~1app2app/get/parameters/0"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "APP2APP Payment Response",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "device": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Device identifier",
                      "example": "352019330429196"
                    },
                    "transaction_id": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Unique transaction ID",
                      "example": "e1d7a4b1-2a8a-43e6-be62-001154f0d2f4"
                    },
                    "aid": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Application identifier",
                      "example": "A0000000041010"
                    },
                    "amount": {
                      "type": "integer",
                      "description": "Transaction amount (in cents)",
                      "example": 100
                    },
                    "currency": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Currency code",
                      "example": "978"
                    },
                    "auth_code": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Authorization code",
                      "example": "247687"
                    },
                    "brand": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Card brand",
                      "example": "MASTERCARD"
                    },
                    "pan": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Masked card number",
                      "example": "480033******0348"
                    },
                    "panExpiryDate": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Card expiry date (MM/YY)",
                      "example": "12/26"
                    },
                    "reversal": {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "description": "Whether this is a reversal transaction",
                      "example": false
                    },
                    "date_terminal": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Terminal date",
                      "example": "Apr 26, 2022 13:44:29"
                    },
                    "date_server": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Server date",
                      "example": "Apr 26, 2022 14:37:46"
                    },
                    "emv_response": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "EMV response data",
                      "example": "{'smartCardScheme': 1, 'authorisationResponseCode': '00'}"
                    },
                    "response_status": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Transaction status",
                      "example": "PAID",
                      "enum": [
                        "PAID",
                        "REFUSED",
                        "CANCELLED",
                        "ERROR",
                        "EXPIRED",
                        "PENDING",
                        "STARTED",
                        "DUPLICATED",
                        "CHIP_ERROR"
                      ]
                    },
                    "response_message": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Status message",
                      "example": "OK - success"
                    },
                    "terminal_acquirer": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Terminal acquirer ID",
                      "example": "M1TPNP0005"
                    },
                    "merchant_acquirer": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Merchant acquirer ID",
                      "example": "TPNP0005"
                    },
                    "operative": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Operation type",
                      "example": "AUTHORIZATION"
                    },
                    "incoming": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Source of the transaction",
                      "example": "DEVICE"
                    },
                    "card_input_type": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "How the card was input",
                      "example": "CLESS",
                      "enum": [
                        "MAGNETIC",
                        "MAGNETIC_FALLBACK",
                        "CONTACT",
                        "CLESS",
                        "CLESS_MAGSTRIPE",
                        "MANUAL",
                        "CHIP",
                        "NON_PRESENTIAL",
                        "KEY_ENTRY"
                      ]
                    },
                    "cvm_type_list": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "description": "Cardholder verification methods used",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "string"
                      },
                      "example": [
                        "NO"
                      ]
                    },
                    "refund_id": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Refund identifier",
                      "example": "128937286421796"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "examples": {
                  "response": {
                    "value": {
                      "device": "352019330429196",
                      "transaction_id": "e1d7a4b1-2a8a-43e6-be62-001154f0d2f4",
                      "aid": "A0000000041010",
                      "amount": 100,
                      "currency": "978",
                      "auth_code": "247687",
                      "brand": "MASTERCARD",
                      "pan": "480033******0348",
                      "panExpiryDate": "12/26",
                      "reversal": false,
                      "date_terminal": "Apr 26, 2022 13:44:29",
                      "date_server": "Apr 26, 2022 14:37:46",
                      "emv_response": "{'smartCardScheme': 1, 'authorisationResponseCode': '00'}",
                      "response_status": "PAID",
                      "response_message": "OK - success",
                      "terminal_acquirer": "M1TPNP0005",
                      "merchant_acquirer": "TPNP0005",
                      "operative": "AUTHORIZATION",
                      "incoming": "DEVICE",
                      "card_input_type": "CLESS",
                      "cvm_type_list": [
                        "NO"
                      ],
                      "refund_id": "128937286421796"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "summary": "APP2APP Payment",
        "description": "La operaci\u00f3n de pago APP2APP permite procesar un pago a trav\u00e9s de un dispositivo f\u00edsico mediante la comunicaci\u00f3n con el servicio Sentinel de Paylands.\n\nEsta operaci\u00f3n puede realizarse mediante dos protocolos de comunicaci\u00f3n:\n1. **Protocolo HTTP**: Para comunicaci\u00f3n directa con el terminal de pago mediante HTTP 2. **Operaci\u00f3n Intent (Android)**: Para aplicaciones Android usando comunicaci\u00f3n basada en intents\n\nEsta documentaci\u00f3n describe los par\u00e1metros necesarios para realizar un pago con APP2APP y la estructura de la respuesta.",
        "x-description-i18n": {
          "eng": "The APP2APP payment operation allows you to process a payment through a physical device by communicating with the Paylands Sentinel Service.\n\n\n      This operation can be performed using two communication protocols:\n\n1. **HTTP Protocol**: For direct communication with the payment terminal via HTTP 2. **Intent Operation (Android)**: For Android applications using intent-based communication\nThis documentation describes the parameters needed to make a payment with APP2APP and the response structure."
        },
        "x-summary-i18n": {
          "eng": "APP2APP Payment"
        },
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "amount",
                  "currencyCode",
                  "identifier"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "amount": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "Payment amount in cents",
                    "example": 100
                  },
                  "currencyCode": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "Currency code (978 for EUR, 840 for USD, etc.)",
                    "example": 978
                  },
                  "identifier": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Unique transaction identifier",
                    "example": "123456789"
                  },
                  "printing": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "Whether to print a receipt (0 = No, 1 = Yes)",
                    "example": 0,
                    "enum": [
                      0,
                      1
                    ]
                  }
                },
                "example": {
                  "amount": 100,
                  "currencyCode": 978,
                  "identifier": "123456789",
                  "printing": 0
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        }
      }
    },
