        "summary": "APP2APP Refund",
        "description": "La operaci\u00f3n de devoluci\u00f3n APP2APP permite procesar una devoluci\u00f3n a una tarjeta previamente cobrada mediante la comunicaci\u00f3n con el servicio Sentinel de Paylands.\n\nEsta operaci\u00f3n puede realizarse mediante dos protocolos de comunicaci\u00f3n:\n1. **Protocolo HTTP**: Para comunicaci\u00f3n directa con el terminal de pago mediante HTTP 2. **Operaci\u00f3n Intent (Android)**: Para aplicaciones Android usando comunicaci\u00f3n basada en intents\n\nEsta documentaci\u00f3n describe los par\u00e1metros necesarios para realizar una devoluci\u00f3n con APP2APP y la estructura de la respuesta.",
        "x-description-i18n": {
          "eng": "The APP2APP refund operation allows you to process a refund to a previously charged card by communicating with the Paylands Sentinel Service.\n\n\n      This operation can be performed using two communication protocols:\n\n1. **HTTP Protocol**: For direct communication with the payment terminal via HTTP 2. **Intent Operation (Android)**: For Android applications using intent-based communication\nThis documentation describes the parameters needed to make a refund with APP2APP and the response structure."
        },
        "x-summary-i18n": {
          "eng": "APP2APP Refund"
        },
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "amount",
                  "currencyCode",
                  "identifier",
                  "parentIdentifier",
                  "authCode",
                  "refundId",
                  "formatDate"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "amount": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "Refund amount in cents",
                    "example": 100
                  },
                  "currencyCode": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "Currency code (978 for EUR, 840 for USD, etc.)",
                    "example": 978
                  },
                  "identifier": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Unique refund identifier",
                    "example": "123456789"
                  },
                  "parentIdentifier": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Original payment transaction ID",
                    "example": "e1d7a4b1-2a8a-43e6-be62-001154f0d2f4"
                  },
                  "authCode": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Original authorization code",
                    "example": "112351"
                  },
                  "refundId": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Unique refund ID",
                    "example": "8237"
                  },
                  "formatDate": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Format date (DD/MM/YY)",
                    "example": "12/02/24"
                  },
                  "printing": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "Whether to print a receipt (0 = No, 1 = Yes)",
                    "example": 0,
                    "enum": [
                      0,
                      1
                    ]
                  }
                },
                "example": {
                  "amount": 100,
                  "currencyCode": 978,
                  "identifier": "123456789",
                  "printing": 0,
                  "parentIdentifier": "e1d7a4b1-2a8a-43e6-be62-001154f0d2f4",
                  "authCode": "112351",
                  "refundId": "8237",
                  "formatDate": "12/02/24"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        }
      }
