        "summary": "APP2APP Get Transaction",
        "description": "La operaci\u00f3n GetTransaction de APP2APP permite obtener informaci\u00f3n sobre una transacci\u00f3n espec\u00edfica mediante la comunicaci\u00f3n con el servicio Sentinel de Paylands.\n\nEsta operaci\u00f3n puede realizarse mediante dos protocolos de comunicaci\u00f3n:\n1. **Protocolo HTTP**: Para comunicaci\u00f3n directa con el terminal de pago mediante HTTP 2. **Operaci\u00f3n Intent (Android)**: Para aplicaciones Android usando comunicaci\u00f3n basada en intents\n\nEsta documentaci\u00f3n describe los par\u00e1metros necesarios para consultar una transacci\u00f3n con APP2APP y la estructura de la respuesta.",
        "x-description-i18n": {
          "eng": "The APP2APP GetTransaction operation allows you to retrieve information about a specific transaction by communicating with the Paylands Sentinel Service.\n\n\n      This operation can be performed using two communication protocols:\n\n1. **HTTP Protocol**: For direct communication with the payment terminal via HTTP 2. **Intent Operation (Android)**: For Android applications using intent-based communication\nThis documentation describes the parameters needed to query a transaction with APP2APP and the response structure."
        },
        "x-summary-i18n": {
          "eng": "APP2APP Get Transaction"
        },
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "transactionId"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "transactionId": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Transaction ID to query",
                    "example": "e1d7a4b1-2a8a-43e6-be62-001154f0d2f4"
                  }
                },
                "example": {
                  "transactionId": "e1d7a4b1-2a8a-43e6-be62-001154f0d2f4"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        }
      }
    },
